title: Awful
review:
The reviews on here are, like many new 'indie' films lately, clearly posted by those involved with the production.

Terrible from start to... well I couldn't finish it. Utter trash, avoid at all costs.

title: ratings
review:
Yet another vote for ourselves rating. All the crew and their friends are the votes here, because the third rate, low budget crap like this would never have 6.9 rating.
All in all, dont waste your time on this awful story, bad acting, worst camera shot and scenes. This is the worst indie low budget crap of the year.
